## Project Structure

```text
icon-fraud-detector-ml-system/
│
├── settlement-console/        # Next.js frontend
│   ├── src/
│   ├── package.json
│   └── ...
│
├── settlement-ml/             # Machine learning service
│   ├── app.py                 # FastAPI server
│   ├── train.py               # Production training pipeline
